item.title: Jacked! Thursdays_June 17th 2010 *PART TWO*
item.description: This is the second half of the june 17th jacked thursdays set. If you like what you hear, and are in the Twin Cities area, come join us for Jacked Thursdays, every thursday from 10 til 2 a.m. @ The Tantric Lounge, inside the Great Sun, off Nicollet and 14th in Minneapolis. NO COVER & THE BEST HAPPY HOUR IN TOWN! Gear Used are a pair of Pioneer CDJ1000's & Pioneer DJM800.

item.title: Intellephunk:Slakk_June 18th_12-1:20 a.m..
item.description: This is my set from the june 18th Intellephunk party, and is a good sample of what to expect out of an earlier time-slot from me. Gear used was a pair of Pioneer CDJ-800's and Pioneer DJM-800. DONT LISTEN TO THIS ON LAPTOP SPEAKERS. BASS IS THE DRIVING FORCE IN MY FORM OF DANCE MUSIC, SO TURN UP THAT SUB-WOOFER!
